      "text": "--> Quickly deploy and manage\napps on Azure without worrying\nabout the underlying infraestructure.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "--> Quickly deploy and manage\napps on Azure without worrying\nabout the underlying infraestructure.",
